TITLE:
	Academic CV

AUTHOR:
	Eric Johannesson

ABSTRACT:
	I'm a philosopher with a PhD from Stockholm University. My research
	interests include the philosophy of science, logic, language, and
	probability.

	Email:   eric@ericjohannesson.com

	Website: ericjohannesson.com

	ORCID:   orcid.org/0000-0001-9128-2565

	GitHub:  github.com/ericjohannesson



