§
Education

¶
PhD in Theoretical philosophy

Stockholm University, Stockholm, June 2017. 

Thesis title: *Analyticity, Necessity and Belief: Aspects of Two-Dimensional Semantics*. 

Supervisors: Professors Peter Pagin and Dag Westerståhl.

External examinator: Professor Graeme Forbes, University of Colorado Boulder. 

Date of thesis defense: 2017-05-27.

¶
Master (*Magister*) in Theoretical philosophy

Stockholm University, Stockholm, Nov. 2011.

¶
Military service

Tolkskolan (Interpreter/interrogator at the Armed Forces Intelligence and Security Center), Uppsala, Jun. 2001--Jun. 2002.

¶
High school diploma (*gymnasieexamen*)

Natural science program, Sunnerboskolan, Ljungby, 2001.

